{
  "id": "prologo",
  "pages": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "background": "assets/episodes/prologo/page_0.png",
      "panels": [
        {
          "id": "pr0_0",
          "characters": [
            "favilla",
            "bambini"
          ],
          "text_blocks": [
            {
              "id": "pr0_0_tb_0",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "Nova Tutinia, elementary school. By day I'm Favilla, school assistant. I handle 50 little hurricanes every day."
            },
            {
              "id": "pr0_0_tb_1",
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "bimbo_1",
              "text": "Favilla! Have you seen my eraser?!?"
            },
            {
              "id": "pr0_0_tb_2",
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "bimbo_2",
              "text": "It's mine! I found it first!"
            },
            {
              "id": "pr0_0_tb_3",
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "favilla",
              "text": "Kids... careful, the eraser is magic — if you fight, it'll erase your toys!"
            },
            {
              "id": "pr0_0_tb_4",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "If only you knew what's waiting for me at home..."
            }
          ],
          "interactions": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "background": "assets/episodes/prologo/page_1.png",
      "panels": [
        {
          "id": "pr1_0",
          "characters": [
            "favilla",
            "lex",
            "mallow"
          ],
          "text_blocks": [
            {
              "id": "pr1_0_tb_0",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "Then there's home. The real battlefield is called Sparkle Ale."
            },
            {
              "id": "pr1_0_tb_1",
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "lex",
              "text": "MOOOM! MILK! TOYS! CHAOSMAX!"
            },
            {
              "id": "pr1_0_tb_2",
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "favilla",
              "text": "Bubbà! Little Ale, one disaster at a time!"
            },
            {
              "id": "pr1_0_tb_3",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "He's Mallow Bellow, the software-developer dad. He writes code, but often crashes the house."
            },
            {
              "id": "pr1_0_tb_4",
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "mallow",
              "text": "Milk overflow..."
            },
            {
              "id": "pr1_0_tb_5",
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "lex",
              "text": "Daddy bug! Mommy fix!"
            }
          ],
          "interactions": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "background": "assets/episodes/prologo/page_2.png",
      "panels": [
        {
          "id": "pr2_0",
          "characters": [
            "favilla",
            "lex",
            "mallow"
          ],
          "text_blocks": [
            {
              "id": "pr2_0_tb_0",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "Explosive breakfasts, endless laundry, toys everywhere. This is my daily training."
            },
            {
              "id": "pr2_0_tb_1",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "Siri: \"Household disorder: 92%. Estimated time to tidy: 47 hours.\""
            },
            {
              "id": "pr2_0_tb_2",
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "favilla",
              "text": "Ale, the spoon goes in your mouth, not into orbit!"
            },
            {
              "id": "pr2_0_tb_3",
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "lex",
              "text": "Rocket spoon!"
            },
            {
              "id": "pr2_0_tb_4",
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "mallow",
              "text": "I just invented the sock-frisbee!"
            },
            {
              "id": "pr2_0_tb_5",
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "lex",
              "text": "Daddy chaos champion!"
            }
          ],
          "interactions": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "background": "assets/episodes/prologo/page_3.png",
      "panels": [
        {
          "id": "pr3_0",
          "characters": [
            "favilla",
            "lex",
            "mallow"
          ],
          "text_blocks": [
            {
              "id": "pr3_0_tb_0",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "But every day comes the moment when the chaos crosses the line."
            },
            {
              "id": "pr3_0_tb_1",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "Toys everywhere, smoking pots, laundry invading the couch."
            },
            {
              "id": "pr3_0_tb_2",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "Mallow Bellow's laptop blinks: \"COMPILATION FAILED\"."
            },
            {
              "id": "pr3_0_tb_3",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "Siri: \"ALERT! Disorder 99%! Evacuate immediately!\""
            },
            {
              "id": "pr3_0_tb_4",
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "lex",
              "text": "TOTAL CHAOS! WINNERS!"
            },
            {
              "id": "pr3_0_tb_5",
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "mallow",
              "text": "The system is completely down..."
            },
            {
              "id": "pr3_0_tb_6",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "Favilla closes her eyes. Two chaoses. A spark inside her."
            },
            {
              "id": "pr3_0_tb_7",
              "type": "thought",
              "text": "It's time."
            }
          ],
          "interactions": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "background": "assets/episodes/prologo/page_4.png",
      "panels": [
        {
          "id": "pr4_0",
          "characters": [
            "favilla_blaze",
            "lex"
          ],
          "text_blocks": [
            {
              "id": "pr4_0_tb_0",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "It happens in a flash. The glasses vanish. Her hair becomes light. A force she has never felt before surges through her body."
            },
            {
              "id": "pr4_0_tb_1",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "Lex is safe. The kitchen is back in order. Mallow is still on his call."
            },
            {
              "id": "pr4_0_tb_2",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "The world didn't notice a thing."
            },
            {
              "id": "pr4_0_tb_3",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "Except Lex."
            },
            {
              "id": "pr4_0_tb_4",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "Lex stares at her. Eyes wide. Then he laughs — that full laugh with his only two bottom teeth."
            },
            {
              "id": "pr4_0_tb_5",
              "type": "thought",
              "text": "He knows. He can't tell. But he knows."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "background": "assets/episodes/prologo/page_carmela.png",
      "panels": [
        {
          "id": "pr5_carmela_0",
          "characters": [
            "carmela"
          ],
          "text_blocks": [
            {
              "id": "pr5_carmela_0_tb_0",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "Across the street, a dark window."
            },
            {
              "id": "pr5_carmela_0_tb_1",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "Something moves in the dark."
            },
            {
              "id": "pr5_carmela_0_tb_2",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "Two eyes snap open."
            },
            {
              "id": "pr5_carmela_0_tb_3",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "Still."
            },
            {
              "id": "pr5_carmela_0_tb_4",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "Awake."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "background": "assets/episodes/prologo/page_4.png",
      "panels": [
        {
          "id": "pr5_0",
          "characters": [
            "favilla",
            "mallow"
          ],
          "text_blocks": [
            {
              "id": "pr5_0_tb_0",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "Mallow hangs up the call. He walks into the kitchen. Looks around."
            },
            {
              "id": "pr5_0_tb_1",
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "mallow",
              "text": "Everything okay? Sounded like chaos in there."
            },
            {
              "id": "pr5_0_tb_2",
              "type": "thought",
              "text": "What do I tell him?"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "choice": {
        "id": "prima_scelta",
        "prompt": "Mallow is looking at you. What do you say?",
        "options": [
          {
            "id": "bugia",
            "label": "\"Yeah. Pasta's almost ready.\"",
            "hint": "First lie. The secret is safe — for now.",
            "goto_branch": "branch_segreto",
            "stat_effects": {
              "segreto": 10,
              "legame": -5
            }
          },
          {
            "id": "mezzo_vero",
            "label": "\"I had a strange moment...\"",
            "hint": "Mallow is curious. The secret trembles.",
            "goto_branch": "branch_legame",
            "stat_effects": {
              "segreto": -10,
              "legame": 10
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
  "branches": {
    "branch_segreto": {
      "pages": [
        {
          "index": 0,
          "background": "assets/episodes/prologo/page_4.png",
          "panels": [
            {
              "id": "bs_0",
              "characters": [
                "favilla",
                "mallow",
                "lex"
              ],
              "text_blocks": [
                {
                  "id": "bs_0_tb_0",
                  "type": "dialogue",
                  "speaker": "mallow",
                  "text": "Okay! How long?"
                },
                {
                  "id": "bs_0_tb_1",
                  "type": "dialogue",
                  "speaker": "favilla",
                  "text": "Ten minutes."
                },
                {
                  "id": "bs_0_tb_2",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "Lex watches her. He smiles again. Only she knows what it means."
                },
                {
                  "id": "bs_0_tb_3",
                  "type": "thought",
                  "text": "The secret is mine. And his. Only ours."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    "branch_legame": {
      "pages": [
        {
          "index": 0,
          "background": "assets/episodes/prologo/page_4.png",
          "panels": [
            {
              "id": "bl_0",
              "characters": [
                "favilla",
                "mallow",
                "lex"
              ],
              "text_blocks": [
                {
                  "id": "bl_0_tb_0",
                  "type": "dialogue",
                  "speaker": "mallow",
                  "text": "Strange how?"
                },
                {
                  "id": "bl_0_tb_1",
                  "type": "dialogue",
                  "speaker": "favilla",
                  "text": "Nothing. Just tired. Come, sit."
                },
                {
                  "id": "bl_0_tb_2",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "Mallow looks at her one second too long. Then he nods."
                },
                {
                  "id": "bl_0_tb_3",
                  "type": "thought",
                  "text": "So close. I almost told him everything."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  "epilogue": {
    "pages": [
      {
        "index": 0,
        "background": "assets/episodes/prologo/page_4.png",
        "panels": [
          {
            "id": "ep_0",
            "characters": [
              "favilla"
            ],
            "text_blocks": [
              {
                "id": "ep_0_tb_0",
                "type": "narration",
                "text": "That evening, while Lex sleeps and Mallow stares at his screen, Favilla sits on the edge of the bed."
              },
              {
                "id": "ep_0_tb_1",
                "type": "thought",
                "text": "What have I become?"
              },
              {
                "id": "ep_0_tb_2",
                "type": "narration",
                "text": "On the other side of the city, Nova Tutinia sleeps. Not for long."
              },
              {
                "id": "ep_0_tb_3",
                "type": "system",
                "text": "END OF PROLOGUE — Season 1: Strange Dawn"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
}